START:
PRC "ENTER A NUMBER:"
REA
DUP
DUP
PUS 1
EQU
JIT CASE1
PUS 2
EQU
JIT CASE2
PUS 2
SUB
SET N
PUS 0
SET A
PUS 1 
SET B

LOOP:
GET N
JIZ RESULT
GET A
GET B
ADD
SET RES
GET B
SET A
GET RES
SET B
GET N
PUS 1
SUB
SET N
JUM LOOP

RESULT:
PRC "THE RESULT IS:"
GET RES
PRM
PRC "DO YOU WANNA START AGAIN? YES (1), NO (0)"
REA
JIT START
STP

CASE1:
PUS 0
SET RES
JUM RESULT

CASE2:
PUS 1
SET RES
JUM RESULT